<br>
The first time I met Master Splos, he was focusing his Chi outside Sol A, bathed in the fiery glow of the lavapool. I felt immediate peace... followed shortly by a nagging desire to trick him into getting up from his meditative pose. At the time, I did not know why.<br>
<br>
