<br>
That is my final word on the power of Master Splos' wiggle. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
*bows and grins and sneaks out* <p><face="comic sans ms" size=-1><b>Shelagh Draigcanwyr, <b> 21st Mentalist<br><b>Rionach, <b> 9th Eldritch<br><b>Tailte, <b> 6th Blademaster<br><b>Member of Cair Vie - Percival<br>        </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub47.ezboard.com/uaalaandro.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aalaandro</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Fluffy </span><br>  Posts: 1444<br> <font color=#ffff00>(3/7/02 3:03:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub47.ezboard.com/faquiloarcisfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=540.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Waiting..</span><hr size=1> I remember waiting outside fear while Splos was training you..I don't remember specific tells, but I do remember guild chat along the lines of &quot;She learns well&quot; and &quot;Miraa's pinching my bottom again 8P&quot;<br>
<br>
