<br>
<br>
I was at a point in my life where I thought everything was against me. This was the day that everything changed. On this Cool Fall day I was looking for something to do as usual. I asked in guild if anyone wanted to do something  and I got only one reply. This Paladin sent me a tell, I had hear many things about him but had not yet met The Great Aalaandro. So we set out to have some fun this day. I cant remember where I picked him up from but we were headed in the direction of Plane of Growth. To spend a quiet day together. <br>
We visited our Mighty God together, I picked flowers with the animals, but most of all I realized that there was still good in this world. We talked and talked about everything. He just sat there and listened to everything I had to say, Never complaining nor judging me. He gave me his opinion, It wasnt always something I wanted to hear but it was the Truth and it came from the most noble person I know. <br>
After our stroll thru the place we call our home, He wandered to Waking lands. Aalaandro needed some mobs killed for his epic but this is where i had to end our day together. This is where I wish I could change the past and stayed to spend more time with him. <br>
But  In the end That Knight and The Preserver married a few months later. And they have what we all long to find, Love and Friendship. I married my bestfriend, My Soulmate. I look back and I know everything happened for a reason and I am happy I had to experience the bad to find the good. <br>
<br>
I also gained the most wonderful bestfriend in Real Life.  With whom I dont know what I would do without. No matter what happens he doesnt Judge me or think any less of me. When I need him to tell me the truth when normally someone would tell you something you wanna hear, He tells me just that the truth and it may hurt but It is what helps the most. <br>
<br>
I have learned many things from Aalaandro, things that cant be replaced by any other person. But most of all I learned what it is to be loved. <br>
From Roch I learned what it is to have someone just listen and care for me in a way I never knew. <br>
I hope that I give him the same in life. Someone who will listen to him at all costs. Someone to be there when the day doesnt go so good, or he feels like giving up. <br>
<br>
Splos, you have had such an effect on Aalaandro and I want to thank you. He always speaks highly of you. He looks up to you with great Admiration. <br>
<br>
<br>
Malasa <br>
